OL,3,CHorizon scandal: Cleared Post Office
OL,4,Cclerk 'shunned by village community'
OL,6,FA former Post Office worker convicted
OL,7,Fof fraud nearly a decade ago has
OL,8,Fbecome the latest victim of the
OL,9,FHorizon scandal to be cleared by the
OL,10,FCourt of Appeal under a fast-track
OL,11,Fapproach.
OL,13,FJacqueline Falcon, 42, was accused of
OL,14,Freversing transactions on the faulty
OL,15,FHorizon accounting software between
OL,16,FDecember 2014 and February 2015 while
OL,17,Fworking at Hadston Post Office in
OL,18,FNorthumberland.
