OL,6,FAt a hearing in London on Tuesday 13
OL,7,FFebruary, senior judges ruled her
OL,8,Fconviction was unsafe because Post
OL,9,FOffice failures meant her trial was
OL,10,Funfair.
OL,12,FMs Falcon, from Hadston, watched via
OL,13,Fvideolink as her conviction was
OL,14,Foverturned.
OL,16,FThe court heard that Ms Falcon had
OL,17,Fworked in the Post Office system since
OL,18,Fthe age of 18.
