OL,6,FHer barrister, Lynton Orrett, said she
OL,7,Fhad given "a lifelong service with no
OL,8,Fmark against her name throughout that
OL,9,Fperiod".
OL,11,FThe former clerk, who had received no
OL,12,Fformal training in the Horizon system,
OL,13,Fhad "no idea" where the near #1,000
OL,14,Faccounting discrepancy had come from,
OL,15,FMr Orrett said.
