OL,6,FHer employer made her pay for any such
OL,7,Fdiscrepancies herself, so Ms Falcon
OL,8,Fused money from elsewhere to cover the
OL,9,Fshortfall after waiting to see if it
OL,10,Fwould self-correct on the system, as
OL,11,Fhad happened on previous occasions.
OL,13,F"At no time did Ms Falcon gain a penny
OL,14,Ffor herself," Mr Orrett said.
OL,16,FPaul Jarvis, representing the Crown
OL,17,FProsecution Service (CPS), which had
OL,18,Fbrought the fraud case against Ms
OL,19,FFalcon after she was reported to the
OL,20,Fpolice, said it did not oppose her
OL,21,Fappeal.
