OL,6,FHe said that after prosecutors
OL,7,Fapproached the Post Office to see if
OL,8,Fthere was evidence to support Ms
OL,9,FFalcon's position that she could not
OL,10,Fexplain what happened, they were told
OL,11,Fthat "there were no issues with the
OL,12,FHorizon system that could possibly
OL,13,Fexplain a shortfall of that nature".
OL,15,F"Had the CPS known then what they know
OL,16,Fnow, then this is not a situation were
OL,17,Fa charge would have been brought," Mr
OL,18,FJarvis said.
