OL,6,FLord Justice Holroyde, who considered
OL,7,Fthe appeal alongside the Lady Chief
OL,8,FJustice Baroness Carr and Mrs Justice
OL,9,FFarbey, said the "reliability of the
OL,10,FHorizon data was essential to the
OL,11,Fprosecution" but the Post Office had
OL,12,Fnot disclosed concerns about the
OL,13,Fsystem to the CPS.
OL,15,F"As a result of (the Post Office's)
OL,16,Ffailures of investigation and
OL,17,Fdisclosure, (Ms Falcon) could not have
OL,18,Fa fair trial," the judge said.
