OL,6,FHe said Ms Falcon had described the
OL,7,F"traumatic" experience of being
OL,8,Fprosecuted and "the embarrassment and
OL,9,Fdistress she and her family suffered",
OL,10,Fincluding "years of being shunned by
OL,11,Ftheir village community".
OL,13,FHad she known what the Post Office
OL,14,Fknew about the Horizon system issues,
OL,15,Fshe would have acted differently, the
OL,16,Fjudge said.
