OL,6,FBaroness Carr said Ms Falcon's case
OL,7,Fwas the 71st Horizon-related
OL,8,Fconviction quashed by the Court of
OL,9,FAppeal, adding that her appeal was
OL,10,Fdealt with at a 30-minute hearing just
OL,11,Fover three weeks after the CPS
OL,12,Findicated it would not oppose the
OL,13,Fchallenge.
OL,15,F"The court has been and remains
OL,16,Fcommitted to the efficient and swift
OL,17,Fdispatch of Horizon appeals," the most
OL,18,Fsenior judge in England and Wales said.
