OL,6,FShe added that recent cases coming
OL,7,Fbefore judges were being dealt with
OL,8,F"under the fast-track approach".
OL,10,FPaul Harris, senior partner at law
OL,11,Ffirm Edward Fail, Bradshaw & Waterson,
OL,12,Fwho represented Ms Falcon, said: "This
OL,13,Fhas been a horrific ordeal for
OL,14,FJacqueline and her family which has
OL,15,Flasted for years.
OL,17,F"She was a hard-working, honest person
OL,18,Fwhose good name was destroyed by the
OL,19,FPost Office deliberately concealing
OL,20,Fthe bugs in the Horizon system.
